posts.post_title: FS: T3 Eddie Collins PSA 3 (Mk) - SOLD
posts.post_content:
Have this nice Eddie Collins T3 available for sale. Asking what I paid....$SOLD.  

Really a great card but doesn’t fit my collection. Corners have some dings and a kid marked a few Ax’s on t he back which is why it has the (MK) designation.  All in all a solid HOFer T3.  Plus it’s already graded.....so you get to avoid that T3 grading expense!

PM me with any questions or if you want to make an offer.

Thanks for looking
